using namespace std;;

int main()
{
    int t;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    
    while(t--)
    {
      int ar[2][4],a,b,c,d;
      
      for(int i=0;i<2;i++)
      {
        for(int j=0;j<4;j++)
        scanf("%d",&ar[i][j]); 
      }
      
      a=ar[0][0]>ar[1][0]?ar[0][0]:ar[1][0];
      b=ar[0][1]>ar[1][1]?ar[0][1]:ar[1][1];
      c=ar[0][2]<ar[1][2]?ar[0][2]:ar[1][2];
      d=ar[0][3]<ar[1][3]?ar[0][3]:ar[1][3];
      
      if((((ar[0][0]>ar[1][0])&&(ar[0][1]>ar[1][1]))||((ar[0][2]>ar[1][2])&&(ar[0][3]>ar[1][3])))||
      (((ar[0][0]<ar[1][0])&&(ar[0][1]<ar[1][1]))||((ar[0][2]<ar[1][2])&&(ar[0][3]<ar[1][3]))))
      
      printf("No Overlap\n");
      
      
      
      else
      printf("%d %d %d %d\n",a,b,c,d); 
      
    }
    //getch();
}
